WEBVTT

00:05:30.160 --> 00:05:32.896
And then he said, "Well, I miss you, too."

00:05:32.920 --> 00:05:35.616
And then I just fell over
because I'm just a mess.

00:05:35.640 --> 00:05:38.880
So I fell over and I sat there with him

00:05:40.680 --> 00:05:43.640
because for the first time in a long time
he seemed kind of OK.

00:05:44.840 --> 00:05:47.496
And I memorized his hands,

00:05:47.520 --> 00:05:52.000
feeling so grateful that his spirit
was still attached to his body.

00:05:53.400 --> 00:05:55.320
And in that moment I realized

00:05:56.120 --> 00:05:58.240
I'm not responsible for this person.

00:05:59.560 --> 00:06:01.056
I'm not his doctor,